---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Real Estate Agent Teneriffe Brisbane | Daniel Gierach"
  description="Daniel Gierach, real estate agent in Teneriffe Brisbane. Premium riverside suburb with unique character and strong demand. Ray White Bulimba. Call 0412 523 821."
>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Real Estate Agent Teneriffe Brisbane",
  "description": "Daniel Gierach is a specialist real estate agent in Teneriffe Brisbane, serving the premium riverside corridor.",
  "url": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/teneriffe",
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Teneriffe", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/teneriffe" }
    ]
  }
})}</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the median house price in Teneriffe?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Teneriffe's median sits above $2.5 million as of early 2026, reflecting its position as one of Brisbane's most prestigious riverside suburbs. Converted woolstore apartments and river-view homes at the top end regularly trade well above this figure." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How long does it take to sell a property in Teneriffe?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Well-presented and correctly priced Teneriffe properties typically sell within 28 to 45 days. The suburb's scarcity of stock and strong interstate buyer interest often create competitive conditions that accelerate this timeline." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What makes Teneriffe unique compared to other Brisbane suburbs?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Teneriffe's converted woolstore apartments are architecturally unique in Brisbane, offering soaring ceilings, exposed brick and industrial character that no new development can replicate. Combined with riverside parklands and a walkway connecting to New Farm and Newstead, the suburb offers a lifestyle that draws buyers specifically seeking something outside the mainstream." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Teneriffe a good suburb to invest in?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Teneriffe has demonstrated strong capital growth underpinned by limited supply, consistent interstate buyer interest and its proximity to the CBD. The unique nature of the housing stock means values are less prone to comparison with broader suburban trends, which historically supports price resilience." }
    }
  ]
})}</script>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Teneriffe</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Real Estate Agent<br/><em style="color:#f5d07a;">Teneriffe.</em>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Specialist property sales in Teneriffe and Brisbane's premium riverside suburbs.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/property-worth" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">What's Your Property Worth?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Riverside character with premium buyer demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Teneriffe is one of Brisbane's most distinctive suburbs. Former woolstores converted into premium apartments, riverside parklands and a sophisticated lifestyle make it highly attractive to buyers seeking something genuinely different.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I work with buyers specifically targeting Teneriffe and the surrounding riverside precincts. That active buyer database allows me to build campaigns with a targeted, competition-driven approach from day one.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The converted woolstore apartments along Teneriffe Drive and Helen Street represent some of the most architecturally distinctive residential stock in Brisbane, and that uniqueness drives a competitive and emotionally motivated buyer pool. Teneriffe Park's riverside lawns provide the kind of open green space that is increasingly scarce at this proximity to the CBD, and it is consistently cited by buyers as a decisive factor. The riverside walkway connecting Teneriffe to New Farm and Newstead creates a lifestyle corridor that broadens the suburb's appeal beyond its own immediate amenity. Prestige values here have been underpinned by sustained interstate buyer interest and limited new supply.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Teneriffe Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Premium Riverside</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Unique Character</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">High buyer demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/new-farm" style="color:#c4912a;">New Farm</a>, <a href="/suburbs/fortitude-valley" style="color:#c4912a;">Fortitude Valley</a>, <a href="/suburbs/bulimba" style="color:#c4912a;">Bulimba</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION: FAQ
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Teneriffe.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median house price in Teneriffe?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Teneriffe's median sits above $2.5 million as of early 2026, reflecting its position as one of Brisbane's most prestigious riverside suburbs. Converted woolstore apartments and river-view homes at the top end regularly trade well above this figure.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a property in Teneriffe?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented and correctly priced Teneriffe properties typically sell within 28 to 45 days. The suburb's scarcity of stock and strong interstate buyer interest often create competitive conditions that accelerate this timeline.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What makes Teneriffe unique compared to other Brisbane suburbs?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Teneriffe's converted woolstore apartments are architecturally unique in Brisbane, offering soaring ceilings, exposed brick and industrial character that no new development can replicate. Combined with riverside parklands and a walkway connecting to New Farm and Newstead, the suburb offers a lifestyle that draws buyers specifically seeking something outside the mainstream.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Teneriffe a good suburb to invest in?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Teneriffe has demonstrated strong capital growth underpinned by limited supply, consistent interstate buyer interest and its proximity to the CBD. The unique nature of the housing stock means values are less prone to comparison with broader suburban trends, which historically supports price resilience.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

